1
00:00:42,850 --> 00:00:48,540
♪Flower petals have fallen,
piling as high as mortal mercilessness♪

2
00:00:49,700 --> 00:00:55,410
♪Gone with the wind,
as if it has never existed♪

3
00:00:56,530 --> 00:00:59,960
♪I ask for more time♪

4
00:01:00,900 --> 00:01:03,290
♪To rewrite our stories♪

5
00:01:03,520 --> 00:01:09,650
♪We travel together in joys and woes♪

6
00:01:10,180 --> 00:01:16,470
♪Blood bathes this entangled destiny♪

7
00:01:17,110 --> 00:01:23,260
♪For the next reunion
in the troubled times♪

8
00:01:24,080 --> 00:01:27,380
♪We tread a treacherous path♪

9
00:01:28,300 --> 00:01:30,640
♪To find each other♪

10
00:01:30,920 --> 00:01:37,600
♪Wars and bleakness,
the bright moon shines upon the city♪

11
00:01:37,600 --> 00:01:40,930
♪I will offer my bravery♪

12
00:01:41,190 --> 00:01:44,380
♪Fighting relentlessly♪

13
00:01:44,660 --> 00:01:47,630
♪All for no regrets♪

14
00:01:47,708 --> 00:01:51,348
♪In this life-and-death battle,
I will not back down♪

15
00:01:51,460 --> 00:01:54,910
♪Withstand enduring time♪

16
00:01:54,910 --> 00:01:58,130
♪Someone at the end of the world
never leaves♪

17
00:01:58,270 --> 00:02:05,210
♪I brave the grim haze
to be with you once again♪

18
00:02:05,210 --> 00:02:10,950
=Love of Nirvana=
(Based on Xiao Lou's novel of the same name)

19
00:02:11,190 --> 00:02:14,180
=Episode 36=

20
00:02:20,130 --> 00:02:21,030
Princess Yong'an,

21
00:02:21,530 --> 00:02:24,150
do you plead guilty
of poisoning His Majesty

22
00:02:24,150 --> 00:02:25,090
at the family banquet?

23
00:02:25,590 --> 00:02:26,690
I do not.

24
00:02:27,190 --> 00:02:28,370
I have never poisoned anyone.

25
00:02:28,590 --> 00:02:30,090
This is a setup.

26
00:02:30,150 --> 00:02:31,150
Do you have evidence?

27
00:02:31,150 --> 00:02:32,590
I found oleander poison

28
00:02:32,590 --> 00:02:35,530
in the Ginkgo Hibiscus Soup you served.

29
00:02:35,690 --> 00:02:36,970
What more evidence do you need?

30
00:02:37,280 --> 00:02:38,650
Official Yu,

31
00:02:38,870 --> 00:02:40,780
when and where do you think
I poisoned the soup?

32
00:02:41,320 --> 00:02:43,480
How long does it take
for oleander poison to take effect

33
00:02:43,780 --> 00:02:45,480
after eating it?

34
00:02:45,590 --> 00:02:47,930
Could it be someone else
who poisoned His Majesty through me?

35
00:02:48,250 --> 00:02:49,810
You haven't looked into all of this,

36
00:02:50,310 --> 00:02:51,750
yet you claimed I used poison.

37
00:02:52,690 --> 00:02:53,690
Official Yu,

38
00:02:54,150 --> 00:02:55,310
aside from me,

39
00:02:55,470 --> 00:02:57,430
have you ever investigated
other suspects?

40
00:02:58,090 --> 00:02:59,150
I remember that on the day

41
00:02:59,320 --> 00:03:01,630
you led the Imperial Court of Judicial
to inspect the scene,

42
00:03:01,850 --> 00:03:03,650
you only tested the food containers

43
00:03:03,750 --> 00:03:05,130
and nothing else.

44
00:03:06,250 --> 00:03:07,980
Why are you so sure

45
00:03:08,310 --> 00:03:09,850
the poison was in the food?

46
00:03:10,750 --> 00:03:12,470
Did you overlook other items,

47
00:03:12,980 --> 00:03:14,590
or did you ignore them on purpose?

48
00:03:14,690 --> 00:03:15,910
Jiang Ci, you...

49
00:03:15,910 --> 00:03:17,780
Official Yu, calm down.

50
00:03:18,530 --> 00:03:20,200
Princess Yong'an

51
00:03:20,780 --> 00:03:22,970
raises a fair point.

52
00:03:23,970 --> 00:03:24,568
Everyone,

53
00:03:25,430 --> 00:03:27,090
the Censorate

54
00:03:27,090 --> 00:03:29,750
has found two new pieces of evidence.

55
00:03:30,530 --> 00:03:32,370
Both suggest

56
00:03:32,530 --> 00:03:34,470
that this case is elusive

57
00:03:34,570 --> 00:03:36,070
and suspicious.

58
00:03:36,470 --> 00:03:38,690
The culprit could be someone else.

59
00:03:39,200 --> 00:03:40,750
Come. Bring the evidence.

60
00:03:48,590 --> 00:03:50,250
This is the first piece of evidence.

61
00:03:50,410 --> 00:03:51,250
A few days ago,

62
00:03:51,470 --> 00:03:54,910
the Crown Princess was also poisoned
by Oleander in the Eastern Palace.

63
00:03:55,410 --> 00:03:56,350
After investigating,

64
00:03:57,250 --> 00:03:59,690
the poison was found attached

65
00:03:59,690 --> 00:04:02,590
to pine and bamboo leaves
as well as plum petals in the washbasin.

66
00:04:02,980 --> 00:04:04,970
These leaves

67
00:04:05,630 --> 00:04:07,430
were specially prepared for His Majesty

68
00:04:08,070 --> 00:04:11,370
on the day of the family banquet
by the Eastern Palace.

69
00:04:12,090 --> 00:04:13,310
Your Highness,

70
00:04:14,590 --> 00:04:16,400
please explain.

71
00:04:24,584 --> 00:04:27,032
The Eastern Palace is responsible
for hosting the family banquet.

72
00:04:27,190 --> 00:04:29,520
I specially plucked petals and leaves
and soak in the water.

73
00:04:30,340 --> 00:04:32,460
If Father was poisoned
by the hand-washing herbs,

74
00:04:32,790 --> 00:04:34,170
I would've been poisoned beforehand.

75
00:04:35,140 --> 00:04:37,110
As for the Crown Princess
being implicated,

76
00:04:37,840 --> 00:04:39,520
I suspect this may be someone's slander.

77
00:04:40,170 --> 00:04:41,440
Is it slander,

78
00:04:42,520 --> 00:04:43,760
or is it your retribution?

79
00:04:45,560 --> 00:04:47,224
Hand washing is only a common practice.

80
00:04:47,670 --> 00:04:49,320
Why did you give Father

81
00:04:49,320 --> 00:04:50,500
the pine, bamboo, and plum?

82
00:04:50,990 --> 00:04:52,950
And why did you serve pastries

83
00:04:52,950 --> 00:04:54,776
that required Father to eat
with his bare hands?

84
00:04:54,960 --> 00:04:56,220
The pastries were clean.

85
00:04:57,160 --> 00:04:58,010
Official Yu,

86
00:04:58,450 --> 00:05:00,010
why did you only test the food?

87
00:05:01,032 --> 00:05:03,010
That explains
why the culprit couldn't be found.

88
00:05:03,750 --> 00:05:05,010
If I were the murderer,

89
00:05:05,070 --> 00:05:06,660
why didn't I discard the poisonous herbs

90
00:05:06,720 --> 00:05:08,456
instead of leaving them to harm others?

91
00:05:09,050 --> 00:05:10,840
Someone must've targeted
the Eastern Palace

92
00:05:10,840 --> 00:05:13,496
and secretly swapped the pine, bamboo,
and plum with poisonous weeds.

93
00:05:18,870 --> 00:05:19,510
Official Yin,

94
00:05:20,400 --> 00:05:21,750
what's the second piece of evidence?

95
00:05:35,050 --> 00:05:36,610
The second piece of evidence is

96
00:05:37,310 --> 00:05:41,010
the Goose Slicing Knife,
stained with Oleander.

97
00:05:41,630 --> 00:05:42,690
It was recently found

98
00:05:42,900 --> 00:05:46,050
in an ash pit
near Prince Zhuang's Residence.

99
00:05:47,130 --> 00:05:48,110
Your Highness,

100
00:05:48,510 --> 00:05:50,400
please explain.

101
00:05:55,220 --> 00:05:55,990
I brought

102
00:05:56,550 --> 00:05:58,750
this knife to the family banquet.

103
00:05:59,400 --> 00:06:00,630
I have no idea

104
00:06:00,808 --> 00:06:02,160
why it was found in an ash put.

105
00:06:02,248 --> 00:06:04,110
Perhaps someone intended
to destroy the evidence.

106
00:06:07,944 --> 00:06:09,550
If this knife were the murderer's tool,

107
00:06:10,010 --> 00:06:11,750
I could've cleaned the poison off.

108
00:06:12,450 --> 00:06:13,780
Why hide it

109
00:06:13,800 --> 00:06:15,048
and draw attention instead?

110
00:06:16,400 --> 00:06:17,070
Besides,

111
00:06:18,070 --> 00:06:19,900
why was this knife poisoned

112
00:06:20,250 --> 00:06:20,990
right after

113
00:06:21,190 --> 00:06:23,250
the poisonous herbs were discovered

114
00:06:23,570 --> 00:06:25,130
by the Eastern Palace?

115
00:06:26,190 --> 00:06:27,950
Is someone trying

116
00:06:28,450 --> 00:06:29,930
to divert attention

117
00:06:30,660 --> 00:06:32,010
and pin the blame on me?

118
00:06:39,160 --> 00:06:40,840
Since everyone has suspicions,

119
00:06:41,280 --> 00:06:43,310
why did you insist I was the culprit,
Official Yu?

120
00:06:43,810 --> 00:06:44,900
If you had investigated

121
00:06:44,900 --> 00:06:46,040
earlier and more thoroughly,

122
00:06:46,130 --> 00:06:48,250
you wouldn't have only
found poison in my soup,

123
00:06:48,490 --> 00:06:49,870
and I wouldn't be imprisoned.

124
00:06:54,630 --> 00:06:55,570
Yong'an, don't worry.

125
00:06:56,450 --> 00:06:58,450
The situation is clearer now.

126
00:06:59,310 --> 00:07:01,310
Apparently, someone
is trying to frame you.

127
00:07:02,310 --> 00:07:03,810
I will uncover the truth

128
00:07:04,190 --> 00:07:05,130
and clear your name.

129
00:07:06,130 --> 00:07:07,280
I'm new to the palace

130
00:07:07,544 --> 00:07:09,070
and have no grudges against anyone.

131
00:07:09,570 --> 00:07:11,070
Rumors about my father

132
00:07:11,070 --> 00:07:12,520
have been spreading among the people.

133
00:07:12,750 --> 00:07:15,900
I suspect this could be part
of someone's long-planned scheme.

134
00:07:17,112 --> 00:07:19,256
I hope you will
investigate this thoroughly, Officials.

135
00:07:21,070 --> 00:07:22,250
I have heard

136
00:07:22,870 --> 00:07:24,050
the rumors.

137
00:07:25,900 --> 00:07:26,990
With Father's accident,

138
00:07:27,900 --> 00:07:29,070
the greatest benefactor

139
00:07:29,510 --> 00:07:30,610
is obvious.

140
00:07:32,070 --> 00:07:34,490
Even if Father is fortunate enough

141
00:07:34,510 --> 00:07:35,610
to recover,

142
00:07:36,280 --> 00:07:37,190
someone

143
00:07:37,780 --> 00:07:39,810
could still frame Prince Qi's daughter

144
00:07:41,610 --> 00:07:42,900
to suppress the rumors

145
00:07:43,950 --> 00:07:45,450
and curry favor with Father.

146
00:07:46,248 --> 00:07:47,610
The one who secretly stirs up chaos

147
00:07:48,010 --> 00:07:49,050
and spreads these rumors

148
00:07:49,750 --> 00:07:52,130
to drive a wedge between Father and me,

149
00:07:52,130 --> 00:07:53,130
you know who that is.

150
00:07:53,400 --> 00:07:54,220
Sanguan,

151
00:07:54,550 --> 00:07:55,900
your greed

152
00:07:55,900 --> 00:07:57,480
has led you to disregard ethics and laws

153
00:07:57,660 --> 00:07:59,430
and commit a grave mistake.

154
00:08:01,930 --> 00:08:02,810
Well,

155
00:08:03,630 --> 00:08:05,510
since you insist
on putting the blame on me,

156
00:08:06,070 --> 00:08:08,550
let's debate

157
00:08:09,510 --> 00:08:11,070
who the disloyal and ungrateful

158
00:08:11,630 --> 00:08:12,950
person is.

159
00:08:15,400 --> 00:08:17,450
His Majesty has arrived.

160
00:08:23,810 --> 00:08:26,630
- Greetings, Your Majesty.
- Greetings, Father.

161
00:08:27,810 --> 00:08:28,570
Rise.

162
00:08:29,064 --> 00:08:30,950
- Thank you, Father.
- Thank you, Your Majesty.

163
00:08:34,696 --> 00:08:36,070
Father, when did you wake up?

164
00:08:36,264 --> 00:08:37,304
Are you feeling better?

165
00:08:37,500 --> 00:08:38,050
Father....

166
00:08:39,768 --> 00:08:41,070
Father, you have a vast fortune.

167
00:08:41,096 --> 00:08:42,952
It's a blessing
for the country and the people.

168
00:08:50,260 --> 00:08:52,000
The case can be closed.

169
00:08:53,280 --> 00:08:55,420
I already know who poisoned me.

170
00:08:55,968 --> 00:08:56,880
Yes, Your Majesty.

171
00:08:57,296 --> 00:08:58,180
Bring the criminal in.

172
00:09:09,830 --> 00:09:10,540
Greetings,

173
00:09:10,824 --> 00:09:12,830
Your Majesty.

174
00:09:16,944 --> 00:09:17,880
Zizhu,

175
00:09:18,904 --> 00:09:20,430
how long have you been with me?

176
00:09:21,830 --> 00:09:22,710
Your Majesty,

177
00:09:22,980 --> 00:09:23,730
this year

178
00:09:23,968 --> 00:09:25,780
is the fortieth year.

179
00:09:27,480 --> 00:09:28,690
How have I treated you

180
00:09:29,020 --> 00:09:30,400
in these forty years?

181
00:09:33,640 --> 00:09:34,980
I'm greatly indebted

182
00:09:35,230 --> 00:09:36,970
to you.

183
00:09:37,190 --> 00:09:39,950
Even if I serve you
for another forty years,

184
00:09:40,050 --> 00:09:42,810
it's not enough to repay your kindness,
even in the slightest.

185
00:09:45,070 --> 00:09:46,020
Now,

186
00:09:46,690 --> 00:09:48,360
Yu was used by Wei Zhao.

187
00:09:48,950 --> 00:09:51,850
I can't stand by and watch my son

188
00:09:51,850 --> 00:09:53,160
fall into the abyss.

189
00:09:55,330 --> 00:09:57,110
You have been with me for years.

190
00:09:57,660 --> 00:09:59,610
You witness
how the imperial power struggle

191
00:09:59,610 --> 00:10:01,480
has wavered the stability
of the imperial court.

192
00:10:03,470 --> 00:10:04,400
Zizhu,

193
00:10:04,830 --> 00:10:06,570
take the fall.

194
00:10:07,690 --> 00:10:09,430
This is not only for my sake

195
00:10:09,950 --> 00:10:11,330
but also for the country

196
00:10:11,830 --> 00:10:12,760
and the people.

197
00:10:17,640 --> 00:10:18,400
I'm willing

198
00:10:19,190 --> 00:10:22,020
to do anything for you.

199
00:10:23,520 --> 00:10:24,210
Your Majesty,

200
00:10:24,450 --> 00:10:25,570
please rest assured.

201
00:10:25,850 --> 00:10:27,850
I know what to do.

202
00:10:28,590 --> 00:10:29,690
I will not step into Qingkang

203
00:10:30,550 --> 00:10:32,190
for the rest of my life

204
00:10:32,930 --> 00:10:33,830
and will never mention

205
00:10:33,900 --> 00:10:35,160
anything about the palace

206
00:10:35,430 --> 00:10:36,930
to anyone.

207
00:10:54,360 --> 00:10:55,850
Chief Steward Tao, you!

208
00:10:57,730 --> 00:10:59,470
You have been serving His Majesty
for years.

209
00:10:59,690 --> 00:11:01,470
Why did you poison His Majesty?

210
00:11:03,020 --> 00:11:03,810
I didn't mean

211
00:11:04,020 --> 00:11:06,110
to murder His Majesty.

212
00:11:06,930 --> 00:11:08,570
I just want to help him

213
00:11:09,070 --> 00:11:10,400
to get rid of Jiang Ci.

214
00:11:12,040 --> 00:11:13,224
Why would you do that?

215
00:11:13,900 --> 00:11:14,810
Your Majesty,

216
00:11:15,450 --> 00:11:17,450
Jiang Ci's master is a traitor

217
00:11:17,450 --> 00:11:19,190
with ill intents.

218
00:11:19,350 --> 00:11:21,850
I advised you many times.

219
00:11:21,850 --> 00:11:23,610
However, you are concerned

220
00:11:23,610 --> 00:11:25,360
about Prince Qi

221
00:11:25,660 --> 00:11:27,450
and dote on Jiang Ci.

222
00:11:27,640 --> 00:11:28,590
However, Jiang Ci

223
00:11:28,780 --> 00:11:30,350
didn't appreciate your goodwill.

224
00:11:30,950 --> 00:11:33,710
She deliberately
took advantage of her wedding

225
00:11:33,930 --> 00:11:36,570
to create an opportunity
for an assassination attempt.

226
00:11:37,050 --> 00:11:39,160
I couldn't tolerate her.

227
00:11:39,520 --> 00:11:41,470
Master and I never wanted
to return to Qingkang.

228
00:11:41,470 --> 00:11:42,930
His Majesty keeps us here.

229
00:11:42,984 --> 00:11:45,070
After entering the palace,
I had never met my master,

230
00:11:45,112 --> 00:11:46,472
and I didn't want to get married.

231
00:11:46,488 --> 00:11:48,968
How could I have created
an opportunity for the assassination?

232
00:11:49,950 --> 00:11:51,850
You are always eloquent

233
00:11:52,280 --> 00:11:53,400
and persuasive.

234
00:11:53,400 --> 00:11:54,730
Of course, you won't admit this.

235
00:11:55,480 --> 00:11:56,190
Your Majesty,

236
00:11:56,590 --> 00:11:58,450
my mother committed a grave crime,

237
00:11:58,450 --> 00:11:59,900
which I'm ashamed of.

238
00:12:00,590 --> 00:12:02,330
But I know Princess Yong'an well.

239
00:12:02,730 --> 00:12:04,210
I can assure you with my life

240
00:12:04,210 --> 00:12:06,310
that Her Highness would never do that.

241
00:12:06,710 --> 00:12:07,550
I know.

242
00:12:09,830 --> 00:12:12,110
Take Tao Zizhu into custody

243
00:12:12,520 --> 00:12:13,550
and await the verdict.

244
00:12:15,310 --> 00:12:16,950
Thank you, Your Majesty.

245
00:12:22,230 --> 00:12:24,190
Fortunately, you woke up in time

246
00:12:24,690 --> 00:12:26,660
and stopped the situation
from getting complicated.

247
00:12:27,850 --> 00:12:29,070
I have already heard

248
00:12:29,610 --> 00:12:31,160
about what has happened recently.

249
00:12:31,970 --> 00:12:33,090
I'm worried.

250
00:12:35,360 --> 00:12:35,950
Yong'an,

251
00:12:36,456 --> 00:12:37,992
I'm sorry to put you through this.

252
00:12:38,830 --> 00:12:41,280
Return to Yuchun Pavilion
and get some rest.

253
00:12:42,360 --> 00:12:43,570
If there's nothing else,

254
00:12:44,330 --> 00:12:45,450
you are dismissed.

255
00:12:46,792 --> 00:12:49,400
- I will take my leave, Father.
- I will take my leave, Your Majesty.

256
00:12:52,640 --> 00:12:53,450
Wei Zhao.

257
00:12:56,330 --> 00:12:57,350
Stay.

258
00:13:14,830 --> 00:13:15,430
Your Highness,

259
00:13:15,430 --> 00:13:17,050
let us escort you back
to Yuchun Pavilion.

260
00:13:20,070 --> 00:13:20,970
What's going on?

261
00:13:21,210 --> 00:13:22,140
Young Master instructed us

262
00:13:22,190 --> 00:13:24,160
to send you out
of the palace at all costs.

263
00:13:28,104 --> 00:13:29,610
Where are you going, Your Highness?

264
00:13:33,480 --> 00:13:35,020
I'm going out to buy flowers.

265
00:13:35,360 --> 00:13:36,190
Move inside.

266
00:13:37,480 --> 00:13:38,950
You like to pretend,

267
00:13:39,430 --> 00:13:40,760
just like your husband.

268
00:13:41,210 --> 00:13:42,020
That's funny.

269
00:13:42,160 --> 00:13:43,430
I don't have a husband.

270
00:13:44,020 --> 00:13:45,550
Wei Zhao's identity has been exposed.

271
00:13:45,730 --> 00:13:46,330
Today

272
00:13:46,590 --> 00:13:47,730
will be his death.

273
00:13:49,190 --> 00:13:50,020
Arrest her.

274
00:13:50,070 --> 00:13:50,660
- Yes.
- Yes.

275
00:13:53,160 --> 00:13:53,810
Let's go.

276
00:13:55,780 --> 00:13:56,450
Go after her!

277
00:13:56,470 --> 00:13:57,280
- Yes.
- Yes.

278
00:14:03,610 --> 00:14:04,470
He's exposed.

279
00:14:04,904 --> 00:14:06,408
All the more reason you have to leave.

280
00:14:06,860 --> 00:14:07,530
No.

281
00:14:07,830 --> 00:14:09,350
He risked everything to send you out.

282
00:14:09,610 --> 00:14:11,330
You can't let him down.

283
00:14:11,690 --> 00:14:12,810
He will die.

284
00:14:17,640 --> 00:14:18,360
Ci,

285
00:14:19,470 --> 00:14:20,280
forgive me.

286
00:14:21,070 --> 00:14:22,930
Instead of being trapped here,

287
00:14:23,416 --> 00:14:25,320
you should be released
into the world outside.

288
00:14:25,768 --> 00:14:26,900
Sanlang hopes this for you.

289
00:14:27,450 --> 00:14:28,470
So do I.

290
00:14:32,480 --> 00:14:33,520
I will lure them away.

291
00:14:34,090 --> 00:14:35,050
Take her to Fangwu Gate

292
00:14:35,050 --> 00:14:36,136
to meet with your people.

293
00:14:36,152 --> 00:14:36,904
Yes.

294
00:14:36,905 --> 00:14:37,500
Go now.

295
00:14:46,570 --> 00:14:48,260
Your Majesty, you just recovered.

296
00:14:48,550 --> 00:14:50,260
I'm afraid that playing Go
may wear you out.

297
00:14:51,240 --> 00:14:52,850
I have been lying in bed for a few days.

298
00:14:53,710 --> 00:14:55,760
It's time to exercise my brain.

299
00:14:56,590 --> 00:14:57,690
It has been exhausting for you

300
00:14:58,230 --> 00:14:59,690
these past few days.

301
00:15:00,570 --> 00:15:01,690
I was just

302
00:15:01,900 --> 00:15:02,980
upholding my duty.

303
00:15:03,900 --> 00:15:05,690
I heard some strange news.

304
00:15:07,970 --> 00:15:08,950
Yong'an

305
00:15:09,224 --> 00:15:11,160
was once married to a man.

306
00:15:11,450 --> 00:15:13,570
Her husband is

307
00:15:14,070 --> 00:15:16,330
Xiao Wuxia from Yueluo.

308
00:15:19,450 --> 00:15:20,350
Xiao Wuxia?

309
00:15:21,570 --> 00:15:22,470
Who is that?

310
00:15:23,590 --> 00:15:26,360
He's the son of Xiao Haitian,
the city lord of Yueluo,

311
00:15:26,950 --> 00:15:28,480
who murdered Prince Qi.

312
00:15:32,470 --> 00:15:33,450
I see.

313
00:15:35,660 --> 00:15:37,980
Yueluo and Liangzhou
are next to each other.

314
00:15:38,570 --> 00:15:40,780
Did you not meet Xiao Wuxia

315
00:15:41,190 --> 00:15:42,780
when you were stationed at Liangzhou?

316
00:15:45,470 --> 00:15:46,930
By Your Majesty's order,

317
00:15:46,950 --> 00:15:47,810
I went to Liangzhou

318
00:15:48,070 --> 00:15:49,570
to collect evidence of Lu Yu's crimes.

319
00:15:50,450 --> 00:15:52,350
I didn't have time to think about

320
00:15:52,610 --> 00:15:53,520
Xiao Wuxia.

321
00:15:54,330 --> 00:15:55,570
But I heard

322
00:15:55,860 --> 00:15:57,930
that you weren't stationed at Liangzhou.

323
00:15:58,710 --> 00:16:01,480
How did you manage
to deal with that rebel, Lu?

324
00:16:02,330 --> 00:16:04,430
To deal with someone
as cunning as Lu Yu,

325
00:16:05,090 --> 00:16:06,710
I had to keep my presence secret

326
00:16:07,400 --> 00:16:08,260
to catch him off guard.

327
00:16:10,450 --> 00:16:12,050
Big achievers

328
00:16:12,360 --> 00:16:14,070
are good at hiding

329
00:16:14,070 --> 00:16:15,400
and being unpredictable.

330
00:16:15,950 --> 00:16:20,850
I think Xiao Wuxia
hides himself quite well.

331
00:16:23,350 --> 00:16:25,780
Your Majesty,
you keep talking about Xiao Wuxia.

332
00:16:26,350 --> 00:16:27,450
Is it because

333
00:16:27,740 --> 00:16:28,520
of Prince Qi?

334
00:16:34,950 --> 00:16:36,830
I don't wish to rake up the past.

335
00:16:39,520 --> 00:16:41,950
But if he repents,

336
00:16:42,480 --> 00:16:44,310
I may give him a chance.

337
00:16:45,330 --> 00:16:47,160
If he truly likes Yong'an,

338
00:16:47,860 --> 00:16:50,450
I might as well approve
of their marriage.

339
00:16:51,260 --> 00:16:52,360
As long as he's loyal to me

340
00:16:52,640 --> 00:16:55,050
and the Liang State,

341
00:16:55,830 --> 00:16:59,070
I'm willing to offer him
a promising future.

342
00:17:06,940 --> 00:17:08,460
Your offer

343
00:17:08,770 --> 00:17:10,110
sounds attempting.

344
00:17:11,050 --> 00:17:12,110
But in this world,

345
00:17:12,720 --> 00:17:14,460
some seek love,

346
00:17:14,810 --> 00:17:16,350
some pursue fame and gain,

347
00:17:17,200 --> 00:17:18,270
while some

348
00:17:18,424 --> 00:17:20,312
only want their long-desired wish
fulfilled.

349
00:17:20,770 --> 00:17:22,310
What do you think he wants?

350
00:17:24,270 --> 00:17:25,050
Xiao Wuxia?

351
00:17:25,830 --> 00:17:27,920
How would I know?

352
00:17:29,270 --> 00:17:30,460
What about you, then?

353
00:17:32,070 --> 00:17:33,350
I seek

354
00:17:33,960 --> 00:17:34,830
a clear conscience.

355
00:17:35,660 --> 00:17:37,960
You have been by my side
for more than ten years,

356
00:17:38,610 --> 00:17:40,490
and I have always trusted you the most.

357
00:17:41,200 --> 00:17:43,900
As long as you are loyal to me,

358
00:17:44,310 --> 00:17:46,090
no matter what mistakes you have made,

359
00:17:46,750 --> 00:17:48,010
I will forgive you.

360
00:17:50,720 --> 00:17:52,220
I have never made any mistakes,

361
00:17:52,264 --> 00:17:53,208
and I never will.

362
00:17:53,590 --> 00:17:54,660
I wouldn't dare

363
00:17:55,330 --> 00:17:57,110
accept your offer.

364
00:17:58,952 --> 00:17:59,570
Your Majesty.

365
00:18:02,088 --> 00:18:03,570
It has been narrow victories throughout.

366
00:18:05,900 --> 00:18:07,290
Well, Sanlang.

367
00:18:07,570 --> 00:18:09,220
Your covert moves

368
00:18:09,700 --> 00:18:11,380
truly caught me off guard.

369
00:18:11,704 --> 00:18:13,590
The situation on the Go board
is volatile.

370
00:18:14,290 --> 00:18:16,350
Perhaps you have too many concerns,

371
00:18:16,990 --> 00:18:19,490
which gave me an opening
to turn the tide.

372
00:18:21,990 --> 00:18:23,250
You are calm and decisive.

373
00:18:23,640 --> 00:18:25,810
As expected of the commander
of the Guangming Bureau

374
00:18:25,810 --> 00:18:27,310
I have groomed.

375
00:18:28,672 --> 00:18:29,960
But this game is not over yet.

376
00:18:30,464 --> 00:18:31,790
There's one more thing.

377
00:18:38,860 --> 00:18:39,860
I plan

378
00:18:40,070 --> 00:18:41,920
to change the Yueluo slave tribute

379
00:18:41,920 --> 00:18:43,350
to three times a year.

380
00:18:43,850 --> 00:18:44,990
From today on,

381
00:18:45,380 --> 00:18:48,010
children and elders
will also be taken as slaves.

382
00:18:48,770 --> 00:18:49,700
Regarding this,

383
00:18:50,460 --> 00:18:52,110
I want you to handle it personally.

384
00:18:52,660 --> 00:18:53,720
If you do well,

385
00:18:53,720 --> 00:18:56,490
no one can sabotage your position
in Liang State.

386
00:18:56,860 --> 00:18:59,310
The last time
you issued a decree to Yueluo

387
00:18:59,620 --> 00:19:02,070
was when you claimed Prince Qi
was murdered in Yueluo.

388
00:19:02,810 --> 00:19:03,700
What's the reason

389
00:19:04,140 --> 00:19:05,330
this time?

390
00:19:05,700 --> 00:19:06,700
No reason is required.

391
00:19:07,110 --> 00:19:08,270
I'm the Emperor,

392
00:19:08,270 --> 00:19:09,330
and I have the absolute say.

393
00:19:11,400 --> 00:19:12,330
Your Majesty.

394
00:19:13,830 --> 00:19:17,250
Finally, you have something to say?

395
00:19:19,830 --> 00:19:20,460
Your Majesty,

396
00:19:21,420 --> 00:19:22,830
I have a piece of advice.

397
00:19:23,616 --> 00:19:24,808
If you stamp this seal,

398
00:19:25,344 --> 00:19:28,030
I'm afraid you won't be able
to face the people.

399
00:19:28,900 --> 00:19:29,860
Is that so?

400
00:19:30,590 --> 00:19:32,570
You have always valued your reputation.

401
00:19:32,792 --> 00:19:34,380
Even if you are willing to take the risk

402
00:19:34,424 --> 00:19:35,810
of implementing this policy,

403
00:19:36,040 --> 00:19:37,030
I'm concerned

404
00:19:37,330 --> 00:19:39,380
that the people will
still find reasons for it.

405
00:19:40,040 --> 00:19:42,440
The rumors about Prince Qi
have already stirred up a mess.

406
00:19:42,720 --> 00:19:43,640
If you apply

407
00:19:43,770 --> 00:19:45,330
this policy to Yueluo,

408
00:19:45,944 --> 00:19:47,310
what will the people think of you?

409
00:19:48,010 --> 00:19:49,960
You said you didn't want
to bring up the past,

410
00:19:50,136 --> 00:19:52,696
but even the Crown Prince has
questioned you in the imperial court.

411
00:19:53,256 --> 00:19:54,900
You just recovered from a poison attack,

412
00:19:55,330 --> 00:19:56,860
and the imperial court is unstable.

413
00:19:57,400 --> 00:19:59,070
Compared to the national stability,

414
00:19:59,490 --> 00:20:00,900
Yueluo and Xiao Wuxia

415
00:20:01,160 --> 00:20:02,490
are not worth mentioning.

416
00:20:04,510 --> 00:20:06,030
Even without Yueluo,

417
00:20:06,460 --> 00:20:07,990
I have more cards to play

418
00:20:08,090 --> 00:20:10,660
than Xiao Wuxia ever could.

419
00:20:12,290 --> 00:20:13,070
Your Majesty,

420
00:20:13,720 --> 00:20:14,570
Princess Yong'an

421
00:20:15,510 --> 00:20:16,530
has been abducted.

422
00:20:22,936 --> 00:20:23,570
Your Majesty,

423
00:20:23,608 --> 00:20:24,776
I have something to report.

424
00:20:24,776 --> 00:20:26,584
Wei Zhao, the commander
of Guangming Bureau,

425
00:20:26,640 --> 00:20:27,960
instigated discord among the princes

426
00:20:27,960 --> 00:20:29,030
and undermined the court.

427
00:20:29,070 --> 00:20:30,456
Please investigate him, Your Majesty.

428
00:20:31,070 --> 00:20:31,860
Wei Zhao,

429
00:20:32,860 --> 00:20:34,380
I have given you many chances,

430
00:20:35,110 --> 00:20:36,770
but you kept defying me for Yueluo.

431
00:20:36,860 --> 00:20:37,790
That's your first crime.

432
00:20:38,010 --> 00:20:39,030
You harbor ill intentions

433
00:20:39,310 --> 00:20:40,660
while instigating discord

434
00:20:40,660 --> 00:20:41,720
among the princes.

435
00:20:42,330 --> 00:20:43,590
That's your second crime.

436
00:20:43,860 --> 00:20:45,310
Do you really think

437
00:20:45,960 --> 00:20:47,330
I won't kill you?

438
00:20:51,570 --> 00:20:52,350
Your Majesty,

439
00:20:52,770 --> 00:20:54,350
I have nothing

440
00:20:54,530 --> 00:20:55,550
to be ashamed of

441
00:20:56,290 --> 00:20:57,590
for anything I thought or did.

442
00:20:59,590 --> 00:21:00,640
Traitor Wei Zhao,

443
00:21:01,160 --> 00:21:02,310
you defy the imperial decree

444
00:21:02,310 --> 00:21:03,640
and undermine the imperial court.

445
00:21:03,848 --> 00:21:05,330
Your crime warrants a death sentence.

446
00:21:05,720 --> 00:21:07,740
You'll be stripped of your title,
demoted to a slave,

447
00:21:07,752 --> 00:21:09,096
and sent to the slave arena

448
00:21:09,830 --> 00:21:10,830
without mercy.

449
00:21:15,950 --> 00:21:19,490
(Lanyue Parlor, Qingkang)

450
00:21:26,140 --> 00:21:26,960
Miss Jiang.

451
00:21:30,488 --> 00:21:31,736
Miss Jiang, you are awake.

452
00:21:35,200 --> 00:21:36,330
Are you feeling uncomfortable?

453
00:21:39,490 --> 00:21:40,310
Where is he?

454
00:21:44,920 --> 00:21:45,832
Commander Wei

455
00:21:47,070 --> 00:21:48,360
has been accused of treason

456
00:21:48,900 --> 00:21:49,810
and arrested.

457
00:21:53,832 --> 00:21:55,360
I'm the one His Majesty intends to kill.

458
00:21:56,420 --> 00:21:57,490
I will trade myself for him.

459
00:21:57,576 --> 00:21:58,530
No, Miss Jiang.

460
00:21:58,808 --> 00:22:01,096
He went to great lengths
to get you out of the palace.

461
00:22:01,160 --> 00:22:02,530
If you go back now,

462
00:22:03,350 --> 00:22:04,850
his effort will be wasted.

463
00:23:19,850 --> 00:23:20,880
You seem

464
00:23:21,070 --> 00:23:23,110
to be dissatisfied with me.

465
00:23:24,488 --> 00:23:25,490
I wouldn't dare, Father.

466
00:23:27,620 --> 00:23:30,160
But you dared

467
00:23:31,010 --> 00:23:32,250
to conspire with Wei Zhao.

468
00:23:33,830 --> 00:23:34,420
Yu,

469
00:23:35,110 --> 00:23:36,110
do you hate me?

470
00:23:37,860 --> 00:23:38,510
I do.

471
00:23:39,420 --> 00:23:39,990
Father,

472
00:23:40,360 --> 00:23:42,010
I hate you for having a favorite child.

473
00:23:43,140 --> 00:23:43,920
I hate you

474
00:23:44,310 --> 00:23:45,350
for never choosing me.

475
00:23:46,660 --> 00:23:49,350
Chi was selected
to be the heir from birth.

476
00:23:50,070 --> 00:23:51,810
You carefully guided him
from a young age.

477
00:23:52,810 --> 00:23:53,610
However,

478
00:23:54,200 --> 00:23:55,960
I was strictly reminded every day

479
00:23:56,072 --> 00:23:57,490
to be a good subordinate and brother.

480
00:23:57,860 --> 00:23:59,530
I live with the mission
of assisting him.

481
00:24:00,220 --> 00:24:01,750
Father, have you ever asked me

482
00:24:02,490 --> 00:24:03,530
what I truly want?

483
00:24:04,330 --> 00:24:05,860
Have you ever really looked at me?

484
00:24:07,290 --> 00:24:09,550
But I give both you and Chi

485
00:24:10,660 --> 00:24:12,770
the same thing.

486
00:24:13,352 --> 00:24:14,250
Do you?

487
00:24:15,380 --> 00:24:17,330
Then why did you appoint him
so early?

488
00:24:18,040 --> 00:24:19,770
The heir is chosen
from the talented, wise,

489
00:24:19,850 --> 00:24:21,380
legitimate, and eldest son.

490
00:24:22,440 --> 00:24:23,380
What is talent?

491
00:24:24,250 --> 00:24:25,050
What is wisdom?

492
00:24:26,070 --> 00:24:27,460
Chi is gullible and suggestible.

493
00:24:27,720 --> 00:24:29,960
He can't protect the great legacy
of the Liang State.

494
00:24:30,960 --> 00:24:31,960
But I'm different.

495
00:24:32,648 --> 00:24:34,110
I'm more assertive

496
00:24:34,810 --> 00:24:35,810
and strategic.

497
00:24:37,330 --> 00:24:38,110
Father,

498
00:24:38,770 --> 00:24:41,110
you decided the paths
for Chi and me long ago

499
00:24:42,350 --> 00:24:43,860
and taught us

500
00:24:44,570 --> 00:24:45,810
to cherish and respect

501
00:24:46,110 --> 00:24:47,200
each other.

502
00:24:47,576 --> 00:24:49,590
Have you ever asked me
if I accepted any of this?

503
00:24:51,624 --> 00:24:52,900
Did you never think to ask,

504
00:24:53,592 --> 00:24:54,810
or did you refuse to do so?

505
00:25:01,250 --> 00:25:02,050
Father,

506
00:25:03,250 --> 00:25:04,490
give me a chance.

507
00:25:04,830 --> 00:25:06,490
I will prove to you

508
00:25:07,660 --> 00:25:09,570
that I'm more like you than Chi.

509
00:25:15,620 --> 00:25:18,720
It seems I was too tied up
with state affairs

510
00:25:19,250 --> 00:25:21,790
and neglected you.

511
00:25:25,050 --> 00:25:28,570
That's why
you caused such trouble today.

512
00:25:30,110 --> 00:25:31,070
I hope

513
00:25:31,900 --> 00:25:34,290
you can return to being the Yu
you used to be.

514
00:25:44,860 --> 00:25:46,070
Understood, Father.

515
00:25:48,110 --> 00:25:48,900
I will do

516
00:25:50,590 --> 00:25:52,010
as you wish.

517
00:25:52,712 --> 00:25:53,784
For the rest of my life,

518
00:25:54,570 --> 00:25:56,490
I will be an unconcerned prince.

519
00:26:00,152 --> 00:26:01,530
Thank you for your grace, Father.

520
00:26:18,400 --> 00:26:21,048
(The Late Emperor; Young Xie Chun)
As natural as water flowing downward.

521
00:26:21,350 --> 00:26:21,960
Chun,

522
00:26:22,584 --> 00:26:23,830
have you learned it by heart?

523
00:26:23,900 --> 00:26:24,570
Yes, Father.

524
00:26:25,330 --> 00:26:26,030
Clever boy.

525
00:26:27,624 --> 00:26:28,920
(Young Xie Che)

526
00:26:33,080 --> 00:26:34,660
It has been a while
since I last saw you.

527
00:26:34,712 --> 00:26:35,830
I have the imperial kitchen

528
00:26:35,960 --> 00:26:37,070
prepare this for you.

529
00:26:37,070 --> 00:26:38,830
Your favorite childhood pastry.

530
00:26:38,840 --> 00:26:40,070
- Have some.
- Thank you, Father.

531
00:26:40,070 --> 00:26:40,640
Try it.

532
00:26:45,880 --> 00:26:47,160
(Chun,)

533
00:26:48,570 --> 00:26:49,880
(what happened today)

534
00:26:50,860 --> 00:26:52,700
(is the same as what we had before.)

535
00:26:54,350 --> 00:26:56,530
(Now that I'm the Emperor,)

536
00:26:56,720 --> 00:26:58,570
(and have absolute control
over the country,)

537
00:26:59,530 --> 00:27:01,880
(however, I have never received)

538
00:27:02,750 --> 00:27:04,880
(love from Father as you did.)

539
00:27:09,960 --> 00:27:10,550
Father.

540
00:27:11,660 --> 00:27:12,200
Father.

541
00:27:16,050 --> 00:27:16,690
Father.

542
00:27:18,590 --> 00:27:20,030
I won the war. I'm back now.

543
00:27:20,200 --> 00:27:20,790
Father.

544
00:27:23,070 --> 00:27:23,620
Father.

545
00:27:25,220 --> 00:27:25,770
Father,

546
00:27:28,010 --> 00:27:28,860
I'm back.

547
00:27:29,620 --> 00:27:31,620
Father, I'm right here.

548
00:27:32,830 --> 00:27:33,790
Che.

549
00:27:46,070 --> 00:27:46,770
Don't...

550
00:27:49,010 --> 00:27:51,030
Father, what are you saying?

551
00:27:52,110 --> 00:27:52,830
I'm listening.

552
00:27:55,070 --> 00:27:55,660
Do...

553
00:27:57,530 --> 00:27:58,350
Don't

554
00:27:59,830 --> 00:28:00,380
hurt...

555
00:28:01,550 --> 00:28:02,610
hurt your

556
00:28:03,790 --> 00:28:04,990
brother...

557
00:28:23,030 --> 00:28:24,830
(Now, I'm a father,)

558
00:28:25,460 --> 00:28:27,570
(and even my son blames me.)

559
00:28:28,380 --> 00:28:29,570
(I have made choices)

560
00:28:29,570 --> 00:28:31,790
(just like Father once did.)

561
00:28:32,640 --> 00:28:34,330
(But there's no right or wrong)

562
00:28:35,330 --> 00:28:37,570
(for what fate has yielded.)

563
00:28:40,110 --> 00:28:42,160
It's a karmic cycle instead.

564
00:29:01,112 --> 00:29:01,620
Reporting!

565
00:29:01,700 --> 00:29:02,310
No sign.

566
00:29:02,312 --> 00:29:02,823
Reporting!

